Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不要着急 仔细看说明书
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,适应了就用专用的笔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在线缝的部位渗线即可
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如此看起来更立体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真实感就出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.84,0:00:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.19,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家回去时注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚姐姐再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我是北条理央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚请做我的高达模型师父
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:00:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来 请看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是高达社区的主街道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 别拽我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.49,0:01:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 就像去游乐园的小孩一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚才是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,居然选这样的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是把以前的试做拿出来的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 不是要给我带路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚明明有账号为什么不登录呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擅长数码产品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,关于对战 也不适应
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来我想去高达基地买模型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然入门级也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是想直接挑战写真级
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要理央开心就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,高达模型就是自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能乐在其中便好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,高达元宇宙正是为此创建的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里是梦想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,面具女士居然是赛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那个对手是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,从头开始讲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道川口女士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,女高达模型师的最高荣誉是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经为了那个称号而战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和妹妹玛丽亚一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,胜者 赛丽亚润月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,成功晋级决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在决赛等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那个装备是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,擅自用姐姐的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还输了比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我放弃决赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要总是可怜我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不把我当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我没那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那天后我就放弃了高达模型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,下定决心放下一切再也不牵扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,远房亲戚的杰夫叔担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,推荐我在这工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只是制作模型就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还是没去元宇宙参加对战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么愿意陪我去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是作为赛丽亚还是面具女士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,以纯粹的热情去漫游高达模型世界的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我在那个世界太有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以得隐藏一下身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但也到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽亚还在恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不能继续玩高达模型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这也太怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不是讨厌高达模型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没资格被称为师父
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我的师父都是赛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不希望她放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,突然尖叫礼貌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,路过的热心姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,放不下独自烦恼的可爱男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有那么明显吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说是有那种气味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无邪的青春芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,吸引了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,来光顾一下我的店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好了走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好好倾诉你青春期的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是赛丽亚的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识师父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,之前有过交际
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫理央
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是马吉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她还在避讳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和玛丽亚沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚是了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是我重要的师父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,为了能向玛丽亚传达我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我要再提高水平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对方可是有实力角逐川口女士的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,讨伐领主的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,里面战斗很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,能积累很多经验哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不太简单
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但稍微有点冒险才刺激对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的眼神不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,领主在中央的天空神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讨伐先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但首先要打扫战场的敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,数量很多 要做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,理央北条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,灿阳高达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,能打到什么地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,又拉了个新人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真乐此不疲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 文奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说得好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是帮帮为师父努力的小伙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,数量太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别说撑到领主了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,上面还有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对付独眼就没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,核心高达
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是创形者的悠人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,和我想的一样 不错的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,战场1 任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色的核心高达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,挺不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你好悠人 我叫理央
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,变形机关和机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这出色的模型是经验和技术的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,随我同去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,此次任务目标是讨伐领主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得组队效率比较高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么和我组队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我还经验尚浅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从你的模型就能看出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是精心打磨的好机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是师父教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,高达从头再来的机会多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是享受过程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好师父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也在看着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也一定会回应你的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,模型也在看着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.67,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,出发吧 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不容错过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可爱弟子正挑战超难的讨伐领主任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 赛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是收其为徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就要尽师父的职责守望到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,杰夫叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是天空神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧理央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是领主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击就像刮痧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那就近战解决它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫 冥王星装备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,核心转换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,着装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,冥王星九型高达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,漆黑的高达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,用回收塑料做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想试试实战能发挥多少性能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,面对如此巨大的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,却毫无惧色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,相信模型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,模型便会回应你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 灿阳高达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,薙刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这边就交给我吧 悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.21,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有撒手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,任务完成 恭喜通关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,悠人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你理央
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你取胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不至于 我能力还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,确实还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不够但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,高达模型会回应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的领主战也燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想和强者过招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来和我神木世海比划比划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,尊者高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,神木世海
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个日本冠军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,世海君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,突然冒出来搞啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想比比打赢领主的玩家谁更强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,赛丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁要和我过招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是冠军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,击败领主的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我想和你对战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是为了变强而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,非常强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正面角力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是模型对战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看着打得挺畅快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,竟有这般实力 真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可以毫无保留地使出奥义了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,灿阳高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,神木模型流奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.19,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,炎王斩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,尽兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你理央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我才该谢你世海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴能和你全力过招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 期待下次对战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,收获不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,精神又提起来不少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 世海太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,文奈？ 不没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,您来看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.56,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,现在差不多可以拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,近期会有大规模的对战活动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,玛丽亚肯定也会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会下战书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我应对玛丽亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.33,0:22:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Comment
